These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-1::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: fantasy, thriller
The people use 2 different means of transport: tram, bike
1. the person watching fantasy movies is on the left of the person driving the tram##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2    |
| Movie-Genre   | fantasy  | thriller |
| Transport     | bike | tram  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-2::.
There 2 different types of food: lime, pepper
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: biathlon, handball
1. the person eating pepper is on the right of the person who's sport is biathlon##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |       1       |      2       |
| Food    | lime      | pepper         |
| Sport   | biathlon | handball |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-3::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: fanta, mirinda
There 2 different types of food: grapefruit, potato
1. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the person eating potato##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |   2    |
| Beverage   | mirinda | fanta   |
| Food       | potato  | grapefruit |

 #################################

 
